Mother's Day is coming up on Sunday, May 11, and you can save on a bouquet from the website 1-800-Flowers when you pay with Apple Pay.<br/>
<br/>
<img src="https://images.macrumors.com/article-new/2023/11/apple-pay-feature-dynamic-island.jpg" alt="" width="1600" height="900" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-921515" /><br/>
Now through May 9, you can get &#36;20 off a bouquet and select other merchandise when you spend at least &#36;49.99 at <a href="https://www.1800flowers.com/">1-800-Flowers.com</a>, or in the <a href="https://apps.apple.com/us/app/1800flowers/id457699767">1-800-Flowers app</a>, in the United States. To qualify for the discount, the purchase must be completed with Apple Pay, and you must enter the promo code APPLEPAY at checkout.<br/>
<br/>
